org.apache.accumulo.trace.instrument.impl

Class NullSpan

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.accumulo.trace.instrument.impl.NullSpan
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Span

    public class NullSpan
extends Object
implements Span
    A Span that does nothing. Used to avoid returning and checking for nulls when we are not tracing.
